 ### Use EnsureCapacity on List/Stack/Queue Before Bulk Adds
 🟡 **DO** call `EnsureCapacity` before bulk insertions | .NET 6+

 ❌
 ```csharp
 var list = new List<int>();
 for (int i = 0; i < 10000; i++)
     list.Add(i);
